IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SEPARATE-IMAGE-1D-TEST.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
SPECIAL-NAMES.
    LOCAL-SIZE IS (1, 1, 1).
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT TEX-1D ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-0"
        ORGANIZATION IS TEXTURE-1D.
    SELECT SMP-1D ASSIGN TO "GPU-SAMPLER-0-1"
        ORGANIZATION IS SAMPLER.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD  TEX-1D.
01  IMAGE-RECORD PIC V(4).
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  UV-COORDS           PIC V.
01  RAW-PIXEL           PIC V(4).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        MOVE 0.5 TO UV-COORDS.
        READ TEX-1D WITH SMP-1D
            AT UV-COORDS 
            INTO RAW-PIXEL.
        GOBACK.
